# BMR export data contains customer PII (names, phones, emails, addresses).
# NEVER commit the data files — git history is permanent.
# Track only this file, the README, and the transform SQL (source code, no
# PII — it reads from staging tables, never embeds row data).
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!bmr_transform.sql
!load_remaining_raw.sql
!bmr_rollback.sql
